==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''[[run]] [[out]]'''
#{{cricket}} the method of getting out, in which a [[batsman]], in making a run, has not reached the [[popping crease]] when a [[fielder]] breaks his [[wicket]] with the [[ball]]
===Verb===
'''to run out'''
#(''of a fielder'') to get a batsman out in this way
#(''of a batsman'') to be got out in this way